📌 Overview

Trip Advisor is a responsive travel discovery web application that allows users to explore destinations, browse hotels, restaurants, and attractions with a clean and modern UI. Built and deployed using GitHub Pages.

✨ Features

Clean, responsive UI for desktop and mobile
Browse travel destinations and attractions
Smooth navigation and interactive layout
Deployed live via GitHub Pages
🛠 Tech Stack

HTML5 — semantic structure
CSS3 — custom styling and responsive layout

